        The Ryder Theme for Hugo
      </h2>
      <span class="details px-6 mt-4 inline-block">
        
        by <span itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span class="author" itemprop="name">Ben Strawbridge</span></span>
        in <span itemprop="articleSection" class="source font-bold">projects</span>
        on <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2024-02-19T22:19:09-08:00">February 19, 2024</time>
      </span>
      <div itemprop="articleBody" class="articleBody px-3 pb-4">
        <p>







  
  




<figure>
    <picture>
        
        <source loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.benstrawbridge.com/projects/the-ryder-theme-for-hugo/ryder-theme-og_hu5f60e37cd498838edbdbc0728d542039_86095_1000x1000_fit_q75_h2_box.d5fa1715830d7297ff370127d1487da64519cb06ef990ac5b252b8a15c6bfe6d.webp" type="image/webp" alt="In honor of this old guy">
        

        
        <img loading="lazy" src="https://www.benstrawbridge.com/projects/the-ryder-theme-for-hugo/ryder-theme-og_hu5f60e37cd498838edbdbc0728d542039_86095_1000x1000_fit_q75_box.848ff1235497c64bd6c4f2bc9c04babbfcd26af08ac21860d44b104a49035e3b.jpg" alt="In honor of this old guy">
        
    </picture>

    
    <figcaption class="center">In honor of this old guy</figcaption>
    
