      </span>
      <div itemprop="articleBody" class="articleBody px-3 pb-4">
        <h2 id="workforce-onboarding-a-case-study-of-ironcove-solutions-orchestration-engine">Workforce Onboarding: A Case Study of Ironcove Solutions&rsquo; Orchestration Engine</h2>
<p>I was hired by <a href="https://ironcovesolutions.com/">Ironcove Solutions</a> to lead product development for a new application they were developing called the <a href="https://ironcovesolutions.com/blog/zendesk-to-okta-as-an-onboarding-process/">Orchestration Engine</a>, an application designed to streamline workforce onboarding processes. We collaborated closely with the team from Ironcove Solutions to bring their vision to life.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
