      <h2 itemprop="headline" class="text-2xl p-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-300 to-yellow-300">
          <i class="text-black dark:text-white fa-solid fa-dice mr-2 text-3xl"></i>
        Pick a Squares Game
      </h2>
      <span class="details px-6 mt-4 inline-block">
        
        by <span itemprop="author" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span class="author" itemprop="name">Ben Strawbridge</span></span>
        in <span itemprop="articleSection" class="source font-bold">posts</span>
        on <time itemprop="datePublished" datetime="2024-02-14T11:30:43-08:00">February 14, 2024</time>
      </span>
      <div itemprop="articleBody" class="articleBody px-3 pb-4">
        I created a pick-a-squares game template, aka the Super Bowl squares. It is still a work in progress, but I hope to have it snazzy in time for next year. Take a look at the template.
Project Goals Ability to enter people into squares Generate random score rows with animated flourish Presentation mode for big screen action with controller to enter periodic scores Calculate payouts based on price of a square Project Timeline Launch in time for SB LIX success Pick a Square: Head on over to the project page 
